<p>President Trump announced the U.S. will broaden operations against alleged &#x27;narco-terrorists&#x27; linked to Venezuela, saying a declaration of war or formal congressional approval is not required and that land strikes will follow maritime attacks . The administration has struck multiple suspected drug vessels since September, actions officials say have killed dozens, and the White House says it has authorized covert CIA activity inside Venezuela as part of the effort . Republican lawmakers have largely voiced support for the president&#x27;s approach, casting the campaign as a response to drugs flowing to the United States .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/7M1yKvv7qebFlq6HjnvJdSe6wq-QeU2TcaiNicSZPJz9JKLrqcmXVhAy4MC2QUDFnLCvTCag1y_IxYNVPvTfvHOxzvo5ZANwvXtFp6-LiqgzC-uFQ1ufft_2B0o1VbeGHGlAc96ShlzFZH6n7l9BrorCtn_hcS5ENngG096oK--s3F8MddTzVOl1eE4sSmoCbWwCswPxvHeuExv9HuVY-3F0t10BkhaSz6QFRwjTyuByhSFyG1_JI-gEK-3mqyfnCwF2Y_MKfqay26TMlg' alt='President Donald Trump points to a reporter during a White House roundtable on criminal cartels, Oct. 23, 2025.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Republican backing: Several Republican lawmakers publicly praised the operation and urged pressure on Nicolás Maduro, with Sen. Bernie Moreno saying &#x27;it&#x27;s important to liberate Venezuela&#x27; and predicting a rapid exit for Maduro .</li><li>Military deployments: The Pentagon has increased its regional footprint with guided‑missile destroyers, F‑35 fighters, a nuclear submarine and thousands of troops deployed to the Caribbean area of operations, officials say .</li><li>Venezuelan response: Caracas has denied state involvement in drug trafficking, accused Washington of seeking regime change, and placed its military on heightened alert while warning of Soviet‑era Igla air‑defense systems .</li><li>Legal framing: Administration officials have invoked links to terrorism and al‑Qaeda language in public briefings, a shift experts say could affect oversight and legal accountability for the operations .</li></ul><blockquote>We&#x27;re just going to kill them - President Donald Trump</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>President Trump / White House: The United States will expand strikes from sea to land against alleged &#x27;narco‑terrorists&#x27; and does not need a declaration of war to do so, and officials say Congress will be briefed on plans . (<a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/video/newsfeed/2025/10/24/trump-says-us-will-expand-strikes-on-narco-terrorists-to-land'>Al Jazeera</a>)</li><li>Venezuelan government (Nicolás Maduro): Caracas denies involvement in narcotics trafficking, called U.S. disclosures &#x27;desperate&#x27;, and placed the military on alert in response to U.S. actions . (<a href='https://www.rt.com/news/626894-trump-teasing-land-strikes-venezuela/'>RT</a>)</li><li>Sen. Bernie Moreno (R‑Ohio): Moreno endorsed using force to dislodge Maduro, saying &#x27;it&#x27;s important to liberate Venezuela&#x27; from what he called an &#x27;illegitimate narco‑king&#x27; . (<a href='https://www.semafor.com/article/10/23/2025/its-important-to-liberate-venezuela-congressional-republicans-cheer-trumps-offensive'>Semafor</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.semafor.com/article/10/23/2025/its-important-to-liberate-venezuela-congressional-republicans-cheer-trumps-offensive'>‘It’s important to liberate Venezuela’: Congressional Republicans cheer Trump’s offensive</a> - semafor.com</li><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/united-states/trump-says-declaration-of-war-not-needed-on-drug-cartels'>Trump says declaration of war not needed on drug cartels</a> - straitstimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/americas/article/3330168/trump-vows-escalate-drug-war-land-targets-were-just-going-kill-them'>‘We’re just going to kill them’: Trump vows to escalate drug war to land targets</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2025/10/24/trump-venezuela-maduro-cartels-war-terror/'>Trump merges war on drugs with war on terror in Venezuela showdown</a> - washingtonpost.com</li><li><a href='https://www.rt.com/news/626894-trump-teasing-land-strikes-venezuela/'>Trump teases land strikes amid stand-off with Venezuela</a> - rt.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theglobeandmail.com/world/article-declaration-of-war-not-needed-to-strike-drug-cartels-trump-says/'>Declaration of war not needed to strike drug cartels, Trump says</a> - theglobeandmail.com</li><li><a href='https://www.firstpost.com/world/were-just-going-to-kill-them-trump-says-he-will-strike-alleged-drug-traffickers-without-congress-approval-13944541.html'>&#x27;We&#x27;re just going to kill them&#x27;: Trump says he will strike alleged drug traffickers without Congress approval</a> - firstpost.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/video/newsfeed/2025/10/24/trump-says-us-will-expand-strikes-on-narco-terrorists-to-land'>Trump says US will expand strikes on ‘narco-terrorists’ to land</a> - aljazeera.com</li></ul>